        <div class="card-desc">Co-created a cross-BU resource establishing how content should be structured, tagged, and written to perform in AI-powered experiences.</div>
        <ul class="card-results">
          <li>Synthesized content evaluations, FILM validation research, and agency audits into a single actionable standard</li>
          <li>Trained the full team and contract workforce to 100% workshop completion</li>
          <li>Developed prompt frameworks and tool-selection guidance for Claude, ChatGPT, and Writer</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="work-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🔍</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">AI Quality</span>
          <span class="tag">Data-Driven</span>
          <span class="tag">RAG</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-title">AI Content Retrieval Analysis</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Evaluated retrieval model quality, content coverage, and specificity, then translated findings into engineering-ready recommendations.</div>
        <ul class="card-results">
          <li>Found 48% of GenAI-first utterances failed retrieval despite existing source content</li>
          <li>Led RAG Ground Truth review of 100 queries with PMs and engineers</li>
          <li>Categorized observations through utterance and response pair analysis to determine the root cause of missing content errors from retrieval</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="work-card">
        <div class="card-icon">📊</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">Content Ops</span>
          <span class="tag">Workflow Design</span>
          <span class="tag">Smartsheet</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-title">Scalable Content Refresh Operations</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Managed end-to-end content library updates for TurboTax across 4 consecutive tax seasons, streamlining the workflows, tooling, and governance to keep it running smoothly.</div>
        <ul class="card-results">
          <li>Reduced contractor headcount while improving output quality</li>
          <li>Built Smartsheet dashboards and automations for seamless SME and video editor handoffs, significantly reducing cognitive load</li>
          <li>Maintained taxonomy accuracy and quality controls across the knowledge base</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <div class="work-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎬</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">Content Design</span>
          <span class="tag">AI Integration</span>
          <span class="tag">Video</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-title">Video Production Model Transformation</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Overhauled help video production, moving from a multi-vendor team to a single-contractor workflow with AI voiceovers.</div>
        <ul class="card-results">
          <li>Cut voiceover costs 40–50% and production time 50% through AI integration</li>
          <li>Videos included in paid media drove +1,047% views from prior year, with a positive halo effect on viewership across the broader library</li>
          <li>Drafted video and AI ingestion strategy to make transcripts LLM-readable for AI assistants</li>
          <li>Launched root cause analysis on watch-through rates and initiated ROI testing for video vs. written content</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 5 -->
      <div class="work-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🌐</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">GEO / SEO</span>
          <span class="tag">Information Architecture</span>
          <span class="tag">Structured Content</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-title">GEO Content Optimization</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Led GEO audit execution with an agency partner to improve LLM citation rates and content discoverability.</div>
        <ul class="card-results">
          <li>Converted H2s to question format, refreshed articles, and added FAQs targeting top traffic opportunities</li>
          <li>Article refreshes drove measurable search gains — one refresh moved from position 8.7 → 1.1 with impressions up 10,747 ITPY</li>
          <li>Explored consolidating 52 state refund articles into one structured piece to reduce content cannibalization</li>
          <li>Maintained weekly GEO leadership reporting using NotebookLM and voice of customer data</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 6 -->
      <div class="work-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🏗️</div>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">Knowledge Systems</span>
          <span class="tag">CMS</span>
          <span class="tag">Metadata</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-title">Knowledge Systems &amp; CMS Work</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Contributed to knowledge management infrastructure, from CMS publishing to cross-BU KMS alignment and knowledge health scoring.</div>
        <ul class="card-results">
          <li>Tested metadata tagging behavior and Gutenberg metadata fields for GEO discoverability</li>
          <li>Contributed to exploration of a new Enterprise KMS for AI optimization strategy, with cross-BU alignment</li>
          <li>Authored support articles for TurboTax AI features (Claude connector, ChatGPT integration) under tight deadlines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

